  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] These all Polish officers got a-- a bullet in the head, and goodbye Charlie.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They kill them all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they claim the-- the Germans do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They do this, and cover the-- kill them. 12 to 15.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was 300 Jewish officers over there, in Galicia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They kill them, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was lucky I wasn't over there, because I wasn't an officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you were not a prisoner anymore?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went out, and then I start to go-- they-- when they went out, they-- they-- I must do something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must have some-- someplace to catch up with something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in-- this was in Rowne, in [NON-ENGLISH], Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They call it [NON-ENGLISH], Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I tried to do something for myself to see a way out someplace, and in the war start-- They gave you papers when they let you out?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they give me a-- a paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let me out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A piece of paper, let me out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My name [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I must find something to do, something to go out, because this area was a dangerous area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and when I stay over there, start the war with the-- all of a sudden, start the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Start a war with this-- with the-- between Poland-- between Germany and-- and Russia, start a war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was official-- not official war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they bombard everything, and I start to run away someplaces.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I run away-- I remember I run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the war start, I run about 300 miles. 300 miles or more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this place-- I remember this place, Wlodzimierz Wolynski.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was a place, and I walk, walk over there, day and night, to this place, and over there--",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
